Title: Empty
Description: Empty tile, used as an eraser in the map editor.

Title: Hookable
Description: Block with collision, can be hooked.

Title: Kill
Description: Kills on touch.

Title: Unhookable
Description: Block with collision, can not be hooked.

Title: Dragger+Turret Blocker
Description: Blocks sight of draggers, spinning lasers and turrets.

Title: Hookthrough Block
Description: Editor tile, places unhookable and new hookthrough to simulate placing hookthrough blocks.

Title: Old Hookthrough
Description: Lets you hook through the surface of adjacent blocks.

Title: Jump Count Setter
Description: Sets the amount of jumps available to you (2 by default).

Title: Timed Switch Activator
Description: Activates switch for a set time (e.g. temporarily activates laser door).

Title: Freeze
Description: Freezes (stuns) for a couple of seconds (for 3 seconds by default).

Title: Evil Teleporter
Description: Teleports to teleporter exit with matching number, speed and hooks connected to the tee are lost.

Title: Unfreeze
Description: Unfreezes instantly.

Title: Deep
Description: Freezes (stuns) permanently, cancelled only by undeep.

Title: Undeep
Description: Cancels Deep freeze effect.

Title: Weapon Teleporter
Description: Teleports shots from weapons to teleporter exit with matching number.

Title: Hook Teleporter
Description: Teleports hooks to teleporter exit with matching number.

Title: Walljump
Description: Allows to climb up adjacent surfaces of blocks.

Title: Endless Hook on
Description: Enables endless hook (on other tees).

Title: Endless Hook off
Description: Disables endless hook.

Title: Hit Others On
Description: Enables hitting others with weapons.

Title: Hit Others Off
Description: Disables hitting others with weapons.

Title: Solo
Description: Enables solo part.

Title: Unsolo
Description: Disables solo part.

Title: Timed Switch Deactivator
Description: Deactivates switch for a set time (e.g. temporarily deactivates laser door).

Title: Switch Activator
Description: Activates switch (e.g. activates laser door).

Title: Switch Deactivator
Description: Deactivates switch (e.g. deactivates laser door).

Title: Teleporter
Description: Teleports to teleporter exit with matching number, resets the teleported tee's hook.

Title: Teleporter Exit
Description: Exit of various teleporters.

Title: Speedup
Description: Speeds up the tee in a specified direction.

Title: Checkpoint
Description: Sets current checkpoint of tee to the displayed number.

Title: Checkpoint Teleporter Exit
Description: Teleporter exit for checkpoint teleporter.

Title: Checkpoint Teleporter
Description: Teleports to checkpoint teleporter exit with the number matching the current checkpoint of the tee, resets the teleported tee's hook.

Title: Doublejump Refresher
Description: Refreshes all doublejumps.

Title: Start
Description: Marks begin of race, starts the timer.

Title: Finish
Description: End of race.

Title: Time Checkpoint 1
Description: Compares your current race time with your record time at this checkpoint, shows how you compare to it.

Title: Directional Stopper
Description: Blocks movement in one direction.

Title: Bi-Directional Stopper
Description: Blocks movement in two directions.

Title: Stopper
Description: Blocks movement in all directions.

Title: Evil Checkpoint Teleporter
Description: Teleports to checkpoint teleporter exit with the number matching the current checkpoint of the tee, speed and all hooks connected to the tee are lost.

Title: Slow Speeder
Description: Causes weapons, hearts, shields and rotating Lasers to move around.

Title: New Hookthrough
Description: Causes your hook to pass through the block underneath. Mid-air, this tile causes your hook to reset.

Title: Directional Hookthrough
Description: Your hook passes through the block in one direction.

Title: Tune Zone
Description: Zone with custom physical properties.

Title: Map: Old Laser
Description: Affects entire map, laser and shotgun beams can't hit the tee they were shot from. Shotgun will always propel the hit tee in the direction of the shooter.

Title: Map: Tee Collision Off
Description: Affects entire map, tees don't collide with each other.

Title: Map: Endless Hook
Description: Affects entire map, tees have endless hook (can hook other tees indefinitely).

Title: Map: Hit Others Off
Description: Affects entire map, tees can't hit other tees with teapons.

Title: Map: Hookthrough Tees
Description: Affects entire map, hooks will pass through tees.

Title: Unlock Team
Description: Forces team to unlock, used in dummy maps to kill off dummy.

Title: Time Penalty
Description: Adds a set amount of seconds to your timer.

Title: Tee Collision Off
Description: Disables collision with other tees.

Title: Infinite Doublejumps off
Description: Disables unlimited doublejumps.

Title: Jetpack Off
Description: Disables jetpack.

Title: Hookthrough Tees Off
Description: You can now hook other tees.

Title: Time Bonus
Description: Subtracts a set amount of seconds off your timer.

Title: Teleporter Pistol On
Description: Pistol shots will teleport you if they hit a teleporter gun block or another tee.

Title: Teleporter Pistol Off
Description: Pistol shots will no longer teleport you.

Title: Evil Teleporter Gun Block
Description: Can be teleported with teleporter guns, tees lose their speed on teleporting.

Title: Teleporter Gun Block
Description: Can be teleported to with teleporter guns, tees keep their speed on teleporting.

Title: Tee Collision On
Description: Enables collision with other tees.

Title: Infinite Doublejumps On
Description: Enables unlimited doublejumps.

Title: Jetpack On
Description: Enables jetpack (hold down fire with the pistol to use it).

Title: Hookthrough Tees On
Description: Your hook will now pass through other tees.

Title: Teleporter Grenade Launcher On
Description: Grenade launcher shots will teleport you, if they hit a teleporter gun block or another tee.

Title: Teleporter Grenade Launcher Off
Description: Grenade launcher shots will no longer teleport you.

Title: Teleporter Laser On
Description: Laser shots will teleport you if they hit a teleporter gun block or another tee.

Title: Teleporter Laser Off
Description: Laser shots will no longer teleport you.

Title: Credits
Description: Designer of the entities.

Title: Live Freeze
Description: Disables movement keys permanently, cancelled only by live unfreeze.

Title: Live Unfreeze
Description: Cancels live freeze effect.

Title: Warning: Entities Off Sign
Description: Warning for players playing in entities, informs that they should turn off entities in order to see important marks on the map.

Title: Spawn
Description: Where you will spawn upon death or joining the server.

Title: Red Team Spawn
Description: Not used in DDRace. Spawn for the red team.

Title: Blue Team Spawn
Description: Not used in DDRace. Spawn for the blue team.

Title: Red Flag
Description: Not used in DDRace. Origin of the red flag.

Title: Blue Flag
Description: Not used in DDRace. Origin of the blue flag.

Title: Shield
Description: Takes all collectable weapons away: shotgun, grenade, laser and ninja.

Title: Heart
Description: Freezes (stuns) for 3 seconds.

Title: Shotgun
Description: Weapon, shoots beam that bounces off walls and pulls the first tee it hits.

Title: Grenade Launcher
Description: Weapon, shoots exploding projectile in an arc.

Title: Ninja
Description: Weapon, lasts 15 seconds at max, allows you to dash, you can't use other weapons while you have ninja.

Title: Laser
Description: Weapon, shoots beam that bounces off walls and unfreezes the first tee it hits.

Title: Counterclockwise, Fast Rotating Freezing Laser
Description: Center of a continuous laser beam that freezes tees and rotates counterclockwise.

Title: Static Freezing Laser
Description: Continuous laser beam that freezes tees.

Title: Clockwise, Slow Rotating Freezing Laser
Description: Center of a continuous laser beam that freezes tees and rotates clockwise.

Title: Laser Length Setter
Description: Sets the length of a laser door or rotating laser to 3 tiles.

Title: Laser Length Setter
Description: Sets the length of a laser door or rotating laser to 6 tiles.

Title: Laser Length Setter
Description: Sets the length of a laser door or rotating laser to 9 tiles.

Title: Slow Laser Lengthener
Description: Causes laser length to lengthen and shorten, doesn't work with laser doors.

Title: Slow Laser Length Changer
Description: Causes laser length to shorten and lengthen, doesn't work with laser doors.

Title: Explosion Turret
Description: Locks onto the nearest tee and shoots projectiles at it that explode. Doesn't work through walls and turret blocker tiles.

Title: Freeze Turret
Description: Locks onto the nearest tee and shoots projectiles at it that freeze for 3 seconds. Doesn't work through walls and turret blocker tiles.

Title: Freeze Explosion Turret
Description: Locks onto the nearest tee and shoots projectiles at it that explode and freeze for 3 seconds. Doesn't work through walls and turret blocker tiles.

Title: Unfreeze Turret
Description: Locks onto the nearest tee and shoots projectiles at it that unfreezes. Doesn't work through walls and turret blocker tiles.

Title: Exploding Bullet
Description: Moving projectile that freezes it hits and explodes when bouncing off walls.

Title: Bullet
Description: Moving projectile that freezes it hits and bounces off walls.

Title: Shotgun Shield
Description: Takes shotgun away.

Title: Grenade Shield
Description: Takes grenade away.

Title: Ninja Shield
Description: Takes ninja away.

Title: Laser Shield
Description: Takes laser away.

Title: Slow Dragger
Description: Locks onto closest tee and drags it until it is out of sight again, blocked by walls and dragger blocker tiles.

Title: Slow Hookthrough Dragger
Description: Locks onto closest tee and drags it until it is out of sight again, blocked only by dragger blocker tiles.

Title: Laser Door
Description: Doesn't let tees through, controlled by switches and works like a row of stopper tiles.
